          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Premium Chequing Account FAQs\nWhat is a\u00a0Premium Chequing Account? A Premium Chequing Account operates just like a regular chequing account and is a place where you can store your money, but with additional perks. BMO \u2019s Premium Chequing Account gives you more flexibility in your everyday banking, including unlimited transactions and INTERAC e-transfers, fraud protection and a $800 welcome bonus plus a Walmart Delivery Pass Subscription for up to 12 months. footnote star *",
